author: olegk
msg: Major changes in the client-side NIO protocol layer in preparation for resolution of HTTPCORE-26
* Added an interface intended to be used to control the execution of HTTP requests on the client side
* Added an HTTP client handler implementation that buffers the content of HTTP messages entirely in memory and executes HTTP requests on the main I/O thread.
